<HEAD>Gas Explosion in Mine Kills 11</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BEIJING (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   An explosion in a coal mine in eastern China
killed 11 people, an official report said Tuesday.
   The Beijing Daily said 14 people were recovering from carbon
