   A 30-second radio spot produced by an ecumenical
media cooperative for broadcast in January in connection with the
birthday of the Rev. Martin Luther King Jr., features his speaking
these words:
   ``Life's piano can only produce the melodies of brotherhood when
it is recognized that the black keys are as necessary and beautiful
as the white keys.''
</TEXT>
